headline: Why Royal Caribbean (RCL) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of cruise vacation company Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) jumped 4.6% in the afternoon session after it received bullish commentary from Wall Street, with both Stifel and William Blair reiterating their positive ratings on the cruise operator.
